ŁIn Memory of
Reverend Charles Rhodes Gott
Retired Rector of Lacock 1932
Eleven Years Honorary Assisting Priest
Saint Mary the Virgin Bathwick
Died 20th January 1953 RIP"┴
ŠTo mark the terms of office of
CLLR CHERRY BEATH
as Mayor of Bath, June 2014 -June 2015,
and as Chair of Council, May 2017- May 2018.
Sit back awhile and reflect, take heart, and don't quit."▄
